    "In contrast to classical RLHF methods, a new line of research has proposed direct alignment algorithms (Zhao et al., 2023; Rafailov et al., 2023; Meng et al., 2024; Azar et al., 2024; Zhou et al., 2024a; Wang et al., 2024b), which optimize a supervised target directly based on preference data, without the need for a separate reward model."
